214
00:13:55,417 --> 00:13:58,504
<i>to find you some guy who's willing</i>
<i>to stick a hanger up you.</i>

215
00:14:00,381 --> 00:14:02,883
[Steinem] <i>I heard that there was</i>
<i>a meeting.</i>

216
00:14:02,967 --> 00:14:05,010
<i>It was being held in a church</i>
