00:15:42,274 --> 00:15:44,818
of feminism and to women's rights.

247
00:15:45,235 --> 00:15:47,363
-What do we want?
-Free choice!

248
00:15:47,446 --> 00:15:48,948
-When do you want it?
-Now!

249
00:15:49,031 --> 00:15:51,325
[Rep. Norton] <i>If you didn't have control</i>
<i>over your own body,</i>

250
00:15:51,408 --> 00:15:53,118
