385
00:24:01,148 --> 00:24:02,774
This little blurry thing right here.

386
00:24:02,858 --> 00:24:05,652
If you focus kind of right there
and you see a little flicker.

387
00:24:05,735 --> 00:24:08,113
-Yeah.
-That's the heartbeat. Cardiac activity.

388
00:24:08,321 --> 00:24:10,240
[Dr. Boyd] The law says
a doctor has to describe

389
00:24:10,323 --> 00:24:12,659
what she sees on the screen
to the patient,

390
00:24:12,742 --> 00:24:14,619
giving her a chance to change her mind,

391
00:24:14,703 --> 00:24:18,748
to see the error of her ways
and realize what she's about to do.

392
00:24:18,832 --> 00:24:20,417
That's the idea.

393
00:24:21,585 --> 00:24:25,046
<i>This is the state</i>
<i>imposing it upon the woman.</i>

394
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:28,550
She has engaged a doctor
to discuss this with her

395
00:24:28,633 --> 00:24:31,470
and help her come to a resolution.

