00:26:23,498 --> 00:26:25,750
<i>a medical question,</i>
<i>a philosophical question,</i>

427
00:26:25,834 --> 00:26:28,378
<i>a religious question, or what is it?</i>

428
00:26:29,921 --> 00:26:32,882
[woman] <i>There had been other cases</i>
