434
00:26:54,362 --> 00:26:57,490
<i>So, we thought,</i>
<i>"Well, John Doe, Jane Roe."</i>

435
00:26:58,033 --> 00:27:01,286
<i>And Henry Wade</i>
<i>was the district attorney in Dallas.</i>

436
00:27:02,746 --> 00:27:07,667
