437
00:27:10,128 --> 00:27:14,549
<i>There was a flight that left Dallas</i>
<i>every Thursday going to California,</i>

438
00:27:14,633 --> 00:27:18,011
<i>and there were usually ten</i>
<i>or a few more women on that flight</i>

439
00:27:18,094 --> 00:27:22,349
<i>going out to California for abortion.</i>
<i>People were going to Colorado.</i>

440
00:27:23,224 --> 00:27:25,560
<i>And a lot of people</i>
