441
00:27:27,854 --> 00:27:31,733
<i>And there were thousands of women</i>
<i>who had had illegal abortion,</i>

442
00:27:31,858 --> 00:27:34,235
<i>who had done their own abortion.</i>

443
00:27:34,361 --> 00:27:37,238
<i>And so we filed a class action</i>

444
00:27:37,322 --> 00:27:42,452
to say that this is a case for all women
who are or might become pregnant

445
00:27:42,535 --> 00:27:45,413
and want the option of abortion.

446
00:27:45,914 --> 00:27:47,874
<i>I was 26.</i>

447
00:27:47,957 --> 00:27:52,587
<i>And I was the youngest person ever</i>
<i>to argue a case in the Supreme Court.</i>

448
00:27:53,296 --> 00:27:55,548
