<i>to make the Court</i>

457
00:28:23,702 --> 00:28:26,663
<i>more conservative than at any time</i>
<i>in recent memory.</i>

458
00:28:26,746 --> 00:28:29,708
[Greenhouse] <i>But abortion was not</i>
<i>a partisan issue at that time.</i>

459
00:28:29,791 --> 00:28:32,544
<i>It was a medical problem,</i>
<i>it was a social problem.</i>

460
00:28:33,002 --> 00:28:34,629
[man] <i>Basic constitutional question is</i>

461
00:28:34,713 --> 00:28:37,590
<i>whether or not an unborn fetus</i>
<i>is a person, isn't it?</i>

462
00:28:39,426 --> 00:28:41,428
